OL,6,FAlice Reynolds, GMB Organiser, said:
OL,7,F"Almost a year since council bosses
OL,8,Fadmitted an equal pay bill as high as
OL,9,F#760 million, not one single woman
OL,10,Fworker has received the money they're
OL,11,Fowed.
OL,13,F"Birmingham City Council owe GMB
OL,14,Fmembers money after years of stolen
OL,15,Fwages, the equal pay crisis only ends
OL,16,Fwhen our members claims are settled.
OL,18,F"This is no longer about sending
OL,19,Fmessages; workers are now taking
OL,20,Fmatters into their own hands.
