OL,6,F"The council has been engaging with
OL,7,FGMB on matters of equal pay since
OL,8,FNovember 2021, and following the
OL,9,Ffurther agreement made with the Trades
OL,10,FUnions in October 2023, has begun work
OL,11,Fon a new approach to job evaluation to
OL,12,Fsettle Birmingham's equal pay issues
OL,13,Fonce and for all.
OL,15,F"The council would encourage GMB to
OL,16,Fexplore solutions working together, as
OL,17,Fit remains committed to resolving
OL,18,Fhistoric equal pay issues, and
OL,19,Fsettling all legitimate claims from
OL,20,Four employees."
